tip.text: Welcome back to Bunga Bunga. Good food, chill out, great music, great staff

tip.text: Mediocre fusion (style), overpriced. Bad ceviche, ok wines. The t-bone looked very good. Service was very good, nice atmosphere.
Very, very good food. Reasonably priced. Very not average Bucharest. This is a wild dorada with fresh veggies and signature Mediterranean sauce.
Fresh dorada and hand cut fries (as fish and chips), middle eastern snack and nice salads..
Good pizza, wood oven, carefully prepared ravioli and cozze, very nice kale and tuna salad. Prices are average, service very slow
Miso is good (ask for extra wakame), also black rice maki and spicy salmon maki. Seaweed salad way too sugary..
With such good food and atmosphere,you'd hope they have the common sense to serve the 4 tables. You have to get up every time and pick what you want, from a wooden menu. No menus at the table. Shame
Very good service, good, fresh food, amazing location
Very nice, fresh, authentic Greek food and fresh fish. Briam (traditional baked mixed veggies) is always exceptional
Vegetarian choices are very good, excellent, very friendly service, great atmosphere, with romantic garden setup. P.s:If you don't love animals, you are not worthy of this beautiful place, stay away.
Excellent as always... Mixed seafood platter, truffle potato puree, beautiful summer day on the golf course, prosecco...
Very surprising in Romania to have such a steady level of quality over the years. The only guys in Bucharest who know how to properly grill a fish. Lavraki grilled with just salt and huge salads.
Everything is very good, we tried horiatiki, the mushroom burger and dolmadakia, very friendly service and great atmosphere and music. Very nice fruit and veggie juices
Stunning views of the Acropolis, good, honest food, great atmosphere and service
Everything is delicious... when sardines, they're fresh :)
Singapore noodles, Asian greens, lemongrass and ginger tea, mushroom noodle soup, good vegetarian choices, very friendly service
Very good dim sum, Vietnamese rolls are yummy, steamed chum soy and celery salt edamame. They also have kimchi but it's too sweet

tip.text: Very professional and friendly, excellent food, fresh, organic, free-range eggs, big portions at very reasonable prices. All day, very suitable for brunch
EVERYTHING IS SOOO GOOD! Small portions but delicious, excellent service, very good music and atmosphere, downstairs is lounge, upstairs restaurant
Good fresh food, wide choice for vegetarians, good service, live music, shisha
Everything we ate was delicious, very good dim sum, steamed choi sum and more..  affordable and very friendly service

formattedAddress: Dubai Mall, Lower Ground, Opposite Bloomingdales (at Doha St.)

tip.text: Lovely afternoon tea set at the Lobby Lounge. Go for the Arabian selection, it is freshly made on the spot and everything tastes amazing...

Quiet, prime location, priced accordingly. For a tea shop,  the tea list is disappointing, with only 4 common green teas.  Surprisingly they have no idea that the water for green tea should be 70°C...

formattedAddress: The Dubai Mall (Mohammed Bin Rashed Boulevard)

tip.text: Everything I tried is very good, have to try the qahwa traditional Arabic coffee (with cardamom) that comes served with delicious fresh dates. Haloumi and Caesar salad with kale are also good
Exquisite traditional coffee (ask for yours as sweet you like to drink it because sugar goes in while it's brewed) and very good sweets
EVERYTHING!!!! Family business, food with heart, grill and cretan specialities, all delicious, very friendly staff :)
Nice cocktails, great coffee, good service. Prime location..
Everything they make is delicious and carefully done. Turkish airlines has the best long haul business class service of all airlines and excellent food.
Dim sum, sea food and sesame&custard bun for desert, delicious. Very good service, traditional, authentic cantonese
Exceptionally good and fresh food, everything tastes amazing, love the cozy, welcoming atmosphere at the grill

Spice Island coffee infusion with ginger, cinnamon and cardamom in the rainforest... beautiful and fragrant environment. If you want to relax in Singapore, this might just be your spot

Excellent service, very nice ambiance, very good food. Try the oysters (any), duck fat baby potatoes and chorizo flavored sauteed calamari..
Amazing view, great lounge music, breeze, prosecco..

tip.text: Honest, delicious Hong Kong dimsum and more. If you're not the princess and the pea, it's great. Very friendly and light-speed staff

tip.text: Good salads, decent size everything. Service slow and careless, prosecco flat and cheapest they could find... They should focus more on customer service, hip places w/o service become obsolete fast...
By far the best restaurant and best service in Bucharest! Try the artichoke and sepia warm sald (off menu) and boston salad, paccheri with monkfish
Good pizza, ask for x-crispy if you dont like bread. Misto funghi and Peppe nero pizzas are very good (so far), friendly staff, cozy seating. Two restaurants in one, serves lebanese and shisha.
Very good dim sum and cold veggie vietnamese rolls. Cold Tsingtao beer :)
Tom yam(my) seabass :)
Spicy tuna avocado, dim sum, tom yam seabass and fries. All Excellent!
Still the best, freshest and properly grilled lup de mare (lavraki) din Bucuresti! Also best price 49lei. Authentic greek salad, good haloumi and tirokafteri. Very friendly staff and quiet location.
Fresh shrimp on the grill and local Alfa beer. Delicious :) Like hot? Get homemade tirokafteri ;)
Nice and Clean! Gotta try the ReserveTM!Generous space,comfy seating,large patio. Staff profi and friendly. I wish there were more green outside on the patio, hopefully they will get it ;)
Nice elliniko metrio and enjoying reading Apopsi tou Notou ;)
Sashimi is very good, gyoza below average, good miso soup, good macha icecream, good macha green tea, ok tuna and salmon salads (simple).
High standards (cleanliness and service) v.good dim sum and various vietnamese and vegetarian menu too, cosy, elegant atmosphere, no fuss for no reservation clients.
Beautiful tuna tartare, spring salad, salmon sashimi with vietnamese style veggie wraps and lentil risotto with grilled calamari.
